    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera S is a benchmark example of naturally aspirated performance. Powered by the 3.8L flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), the powerplant offers exceptional throttle response and linear torque. The 6-speed manual transaxle provides precise shift throws, complemented by a factory limited-slip differential. This chassis is equipped with the Sport Chrono Package and Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), allowing for fine-tuned damping and aggressive mapping. The vehicle is mechanically flawless, showing no signs of rear main seal weeping or bore scoring. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, while the cabin remains free of bolster wear or switchgear delamination. Full service documentation confirms meticulous preventative maintenance.",
      "price": 44500.0,
