      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no swirl marks, chips, or dings. Inside, the premium leather upholstery remains supple and carries that distinct new-car scent, completely free from any wear, creasing, or fading. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the driver-assist features, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive maintenance log included. It has been meticulously garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never been driven in inclement weather. Included with the sale are both original keys, all factory manuals, and a custom-fitted car cover. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector to own a flawless example of automotive excellence.",
